name: Warung Padi Selera Nusantara
address: G34G+7GG, Jalan Desa, Gadungan, Kec. Selemadeg Tim., Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82161, Indonesia
review 1: Nice retreat for recreation, pool, music, karaoke and honest cheap food and drinks, managed by mr Giri, born in Gadungan, which invites for quiet motorbiking through beautiful paddies and hidden villages.
review 2: Wonderful place... It's a resto with swimming pool and billiard table included. Pricing is very nice, and the overall atmosphere is comfortable. The place is suitable for all ages, it has even kids playground! The swimming pool is also not too deep for kids, maybe you can take your kid swimming in this resto of which is located in a usually hot and dry condition in the noon, which is perfect! As for dishes and beverages, I reommend to try the Nasi Genyol (Rice+Pork+Lawar+Vegetables) and the Milo Ice.
review 3: Suitable place for hanging out and to have community meeting especially for Tourism Group in Tabanan. Focus Discussion Group of small pax is held here in Selemadeg Timur with nice view of paddyfield and sustainable constructions from simple wooden or bamboo material.
review 4: affordable food. Nice view when its not too sunny of a day. They are making a swimming pool for public now. Ayam tempong is best üëç
